 <title>&kw-hos-tm; 5.0: Key Manager Service (Barbican) Features</title>
 <para>
  Key Manager Service (Barbican) produces a secret storage and generation
  system capable of providing key management for services wishing to enable
  encryption features.
 </para>
 <para>
  Barbican is all new for the &kw-hos; Mitaka release.
 </para>
